        <b>Source:</b> SRC-0001<br/>
        <b>Confidence:</b> high<br/>
        <b>Notes:</b> Official report lists IGARI coordinate as 065612N 1033506E; MH370 passed IGARI at 1720:31 UTC.
      ]]></description>
      <Point>
        <coordinates>103.585000,6.936667,0</coordinates>
      </Point>
    </Placemark>
    <Placemark>
      <name>IKUKO</name>
      <description><![CDATA[
        <b>Source:</b> SRC-0001<br/>
        <b>Confidence:</b> high<br/>
        <b>Notes:</b> Official report lists IKUKO coordinate as 054512N 1031324E; route segment R208 between IKUKO and IGARI.
      ]]></description>
